data.description: Will Not Last Long!! AS-IS, NO Repairs will Be Made.  Some Cosmetic upgrades needed.   This is your opportunity to make a house a home. The perfect opportunity is here. With some TLC this home can shine! This home is tucked in a quiet and lovely Windbrook neighborhood in Clinton, MD. This home offers 4 bedrooms 2 full bathrooms 1640sq ft total. On the main level, you are greeted with beautiful carpeted floors in a great open airy living room New doors and some interior upgrades have recently been done. The Basement features three bedrooms and a shared bathroom. The upper-level Houses 1 bedroom and a very cozy bathroom. The yard is very spacious and super nice to host events for family and friends. Located near the Andrews Air Force Base and off Branch ave and Route 5. The property is ready to be yours. Bring your Best Offer as this Home is Boosting with Equity!!!
